187
00:09:20.894 --> 00:09:22.519
Sunshine in a rock.

188
00:09:22.520 --> 00:09:23.896
Well. no. 'cause yesterday at lunch.

189
00:09:23.897 --> 00:09:25.814
Becca was being. like. such a... Yeah.

190
00:09:25.815 --> 00:09:27.817
