- Ian told me you were freaked out.

780
00:36:19.969 --> 00:36:23.680
I'm just glad I could be there. I guess.

781
00:36:23.681 --> 00:36:28.311
Yeah. um. so I probably shouldn't have taken anything.

782
00:36:31.898 --> 00:36:33.774
So...

783
00:36:33.775 --> 00:36:36.444
I was on MDMA.

784
00:36:37.278 --> 00:36:40.322
