stuff?

789
00:36:50.583 --> 00:36:52.960
Some of it. I mean...

790
00:36:52.961 --> 00:36:56.213
So. if I was weird. that's why. and my dad made me a mess.

791
00:36:56.214 --> 00:36:58.424
and so I did things I probably
wouldn't have done otherwise.

792
00:36:58.425 --> 00:37:00.342
And I'm not saying that you took advantage of me.

793
00:37:00.343 --> 00:37:03.011
Nikki. I didn't know you were on drugs.

794
00:37:03.012 --> 00:37:04.638
That's what I'm saying. I'm not saying that.

795
00:37:04.639 --> 00:37:06.932
