972
00:48:44.672 --> 00:48:46.382
For Sandy. okay?

973
00:48:52.805 --> 00:48:55.057
♪♪

974
00:49:13.868 --> 00:49:16.453
Stay!

975
00:49:20.749 --> 00:49:22.960
